headline: Scott Foster, CPA, MBA, Joins Sightview as Chief Financial Officer
summary: DURHAM, N.C., October 28, 2025--Sightview, the only electronic health record and practice management partner focused solely on eyecare, has appointed D. Scott Foster (Scott), CPA, MBA, as chief financial officer. With more than thirty years of experience in healthcare finance, Scott joins Sightview as the organization continues to reshape itself for the future of eyecare.
